  "keyFeatures": [
    "LSM-tree storage engine built on object storage (S3, GCS, Azure)",
    "ACID transactions with configurable isolation levels",
    "Snapshots and checkpoints for consistent point-in-time reads",
    "Range queries with efficient scanning",
    "Automatic compaction and garbage collection",
    "Change data capture (CDC) for streaming updates",
    "Multiple compression algorithms (Snappy, LZ4, Zstd)",
    "Block and disk caching for performance optimization",
    "Merge operators for atomic read-modify-write",
    "Language bindings for Rust, Go, Java, and Python"
  ],
